title: Soner Uysal
text:
Soner Uysal (born 24 August 1977) is a Turkish <a href="association%20football">football</a> coach and a former player.
He had to retire at just 24 years of age due to chronic knee injury. In March 2018, he became assistant coach at <a href="Hamburger%20SV">Hamburger SV</a>. He also holds German citizenship.
